<p>The niece of billionaire businessman and casino baron James Packer did flash some cash recently. </p>

<p>She reportedly set a new record, spending more than half a million at a recent jewellery auction. </p>

<p>Private Sydney claimed the heiress was the mystery bidder of a stunning diamond ring, which went under the hammer by auction house Leonard Joel.</p>

<p>The brunette beauty, who counts PR queen Roxy Jacenko as one of her famous friends, reportedly dropped a cool $575,000 for the emerald cut diamond. </p>

